Oct. 27. 2015
	 1. Created a Rails Application:
	 	Terminal Command: 
	 		rails new Depot
	 2. Created the database using Scaffold. 
	 	It will generate both Data Table,a Model and a controller.  
	 	I'm using SQLite3. 
	 	Terminal Command: 
	 		rails generate scaffold post title:string text:text
	 		
	 		rails generate model comment post_id:integer text:text

	 		rails db:migrate
